Description:
Imagining a scenery where you walk around in France’s famous alleys in your EMMA, exploring the fine life you so deserve.

The harmony of French delicacy and romance exquisitely portrayed in this gorgeous piece.

Crafted from an ethereal satin pleat fabric that enriches your look, and a design highlighting femininity and the epitome of simple elegance.

It’s that “je ne sais quoi” flair you need in your wardrobe.

