A fine fabric exclusively weaved for EMMA. The softness of each thread will feel so comforting on your skin.

A beautiful embroidery inspired pattern, in a breathtaking rose color with white embroidery accents of paisley &amp; hearts.

&nbsp;

Note: due to natural nature of the fabric, it may shrink a few centimeters after wash.
